CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 25, 1960, pg. A11 reads: "3. Representative Jerry Killeen, Andy Sanderback, BIll Carter and Claire Dobson smile happily for the photographer from their Hawkinson Treads Inc. booth, which displayed the General Tire"
TitMainTitle: Andy Sanderback, Jerry Killeen, and Claire Dobson, posed in Hawkinson Treads, Incorporated booth in Syria Mosque for the 1960 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama
